{"tid":861380,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[CUTE] TWICE多賢的眼睛是裝了紅外線嗎？神一般的鏡頭認知能力！","createTime":"2018-10-14T05:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T16:48:01.000Z","uid":74065,"like":32,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"73c44e39e822ea5618fe337a556a79d2211fef74","tid":861380,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_4e5ed3a46447569e8d391cd21afb17bd/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-11/110173-664466.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_4e5ed3a46447569e8d391cd21afb17bd%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-11%2F110173-664466.png&h=6d78d020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據說藝人當久了會不自覺的尋找鏡頭，而TWICE成員多賢可能是天生對鏡頭有著敏銳的察覺力，時刻都能找到鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n隨時隨地找到粉絲和舞台上的鏡頭，並給出正確的反應！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_39e65aa6977bb15346d525afa81c765d/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-11/110173-664445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_39e65aa6977bb15346d525afa81c765d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-11%2F110173-664445.jpg&h=625d8cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b6267727d3055a5625f9a09d1e33e952/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-11/110173-664446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b6267727d3055a5625f9a09d1e33e952%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-11%2F110173-664446.jpg&h=aafce0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哪怕再~~~遠都能準確無誤地感知到！多賢啊，你是不是裝了紅外線探測儀呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6d2eeed7013fb1bd778036caab91bbb3/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-11/110173-664449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6d2eeed7013fb1bd778036caab91bbb3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-11%2F110173-664449.jpg&h=10a97ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這麼長的隊伍，這麼遠的距離，你是怎麼做做到的？？<br />\n<img src